Package: spANOVA
Type: Package
Title: An R package to perform analysis of experiments with spatial dependence
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lucas Roberto de Castro, Diogo Francisco Rossoni, Renato Ribeiro de Lima
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package provides functions to perform analysis of variance when the experimental units are spatially correlated. There are two methods to deal with spatial dependence: Autoregressive models and geostatistics. For both methods, there is three multicomparison procedure available: Tukey, multivariate T, and Scott-Knott.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
